message.content: cs.DB, cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.IR, cs.SE. The paper discusses the impact of Jeff Naughton's work on the database research field, which is primarily covered by the cs.DB sub-category. However, Naughton's work has also touched on topics such as cryptography (cs.CR), data structures (cs.DS), information retrieval (cs.IR), and software engineering (cs.SE), making these sub-categories also likely candidates.
